description: After an easy chicken recipe? Try this traybake that's full of veggies, honey soy chicken and noodles, and takes only 20 minutes to make.
name: Chicken, veggie & noodle traybake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500 g pkt Woolworths COOK honey soy chicken breast strips
450 g pkt Woolworths COOK stir fry hokkien noodles

recipeInstructions.text: Meanwhile, place noodles in a heatproof bowl and cover with boiling water. Stand for 3 minutes. Drain, reserving 2 tbs cooking liquid. Add noodles, reserved cooking liquid and choy sum to tray and toss to coat. Bake for 5 minutes or until vegetables are tender. Divide among bowls and serve scattered with sesame seeds and coriander.
